div.blog.mdl-layout.mdl-js-layout(:style='{backgroundImage}')
    div.mdl-layout__content(v-if='backgroundImage')
        h1.text-center.readable.mdl-color-text--grey-50 {{title}}
        h2.text-center.readable.mdl-color-text--grey-100 {{description}}
        div.blog__posts.mdl-grid
            blog-post(v-for="blogPost in blogPosts", :blogPost="blogPost")
            div.mdl-card.coffee-pic.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--8-col
                div.mdl-card__media.mdl-color-text--grey-50
                    h3
                        a(href='entry.html') Coffee Pic
                div.mdl-card__supporting-text.meta.mdl-color-text--grey-600
                    div.minilogo
                    div
                        strong The Newist
                        span 2 days ago
            div.mdl-card.something-else.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--8-col.mdl-cell--4-col-desktop
                div.mdl-card__media.mdl-color-text--grey-50
                    h3
                        a(href='entry.html') Lakeside Pic
                div.mdl-card__supporting-text.meta.mdl-color-text--grey-600
                    div.minilogo
                    div
                        strong The Newist
                        span 2 days ago
            div.mdl-card.on-the-road-again.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--12-col
                div.mdl-card__media.mdl-color-text--grey-50
                    h3
                        a(href='entry.html') On the road again
                div.mdl-color-text--grey-600.mdl-card__supporting-text
                    | Enim labore aliqua consequat ut quis ad occaecat aliquip incididunt. Sunt nulla eu enim irure enim nostrud aliqua consectetur ad consectetur sunt ullamco officia. Ex officia laborum et consequat duis.
                div.mdl-card__supporting-text.meta.mdl-color-text--grey-600
                    div.minilogo
                    div
                        strong The Newist
                        span 2 days ago
            div.mdl-card.shopping.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--12-col
                div.mdl-card__media.mdl-color-text--grey-50
                    h3
                        a(href='entry.html') Shopping
                div.mdl-card__supporting-text.mdl-color-text--grey-600
                    | Enim labore aliqua consequat ut quis ad occaecat aliquip incididunt. Sunt nulla eu enim irure enim nostrud aliqua consectetur ad consectetur sunt ullamco officia. Ex officia laborum et consequat duis.
                div.mdl-card__supporting-text.meta.mdl-color-text--grey-600
                    div.minilogo
                    div
                        strong The Newist
                        span 2 days ago
            nav.demo-nav.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--12-col
                div.section-spacer
                a.demo-nav__button(href='entry.html', title='show more')
                    | More
                    button.mdl-button.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--icon
                        i.material-icons(role='presentation') arrow_forward
        footer.mdl-mini-footer
            div.mdl-mini-footer--left-section
                button.mdl-mini-footer--social-btn.social-btn.social-btn__twitter
                    span.visuallyhidden Twitter
                button.mdl-mini-footer--social-btn.social-btn.social-btn__blogger
                    span.visuallyhidden Facebook
                button.mdl-mini-footer--social-btn.social-btn.social-btn__gplus
                    span.visuallyhidden Google Plus
            div.mdl-mini-footer--right-section
                button.mdl-mini-footer--social-btn.social-btn__share
                    i.material-icons(role='presentation') share
                    span.visuallyhidden share

        mdl-fab-flinger
            mdl-button#compose.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--accent(fab)
                i.material-icons edit
            div.mdl-tooltip.mdl-tooltip--left(data-mdl-for="compose") Compose
            mdl-button#upload.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--accent(@click.native='addUpload', fab)
                i.material-icons cloud_upload
            div.mdl-tooltip.mdl-tooltip--left(data-mdl-for="upload") Upload
            mdl-button#settings.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--accent(fab)
                i.material-icons settings
            div.mdl-tooltip.mdl-tooltip--left(data-mdl-for="settings") Settings

    div(v-else='backgroundImage') Loading...